metadata.name: Protector of Prey #1/125
metadata.description:
Inside the belly of the beast or the mysterious woman's golden cage built just for me? Both sound suspiciously culprit, but in the end I found myself dancing with happy feet protected behind golden bars that promised to open when I was ready to fly on my own. 
01/04/2023  
B Son's first manifold contract ever and first list of 2023. 
3200 x 4500 px  
300 DPI
